column1: league - APFA or NFL or AFL
from - year of initial NFL season (1970 would mean the 1970 season)
to - last year of NFL season (all current teams default to 2017)
seasons - number of AFL or NFL playoff appearances including 2016 season
div - number of AFL or NFL division titles including 2016 season
conf - number of AFL or NFL conference titles including 2016 season
league_champ - number of AFL or NFL champions including 2016 season
sb_champ - number of Super Bowl champions
